{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/shader_programming_intro_3/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>본 포스팅은 Pope Kim의 『셰이더 프로그래밍 입문 (한빛미디어, 2012)』의 Part 1의 Chapter 3에 해당하는 내용(p. 75-92)을 요약하기 위해 작성되었다.</p>\n<h2>학습 목표</h2>\n<p>셰이더를 통해 모델에 텍스처를 입히는 텍스처매핑(texture mapping)을 구현하고 이 원리를 이해한다.</p>\n<h2>텍스처매핑 구현하기</h2>\n<p>편의를 위해 \"<a href=\"https://sungkukpark.github.io/shader_programming_intro_2/\">진짜 쉬운 빨강 셰이더</a>\"의 완성 시점부터 텍스처 매핑을 구현해보자. 만약 아직 렌더몽키와 HLSL 기초 문법을 숙지하지 못했다면 링크된 페이지를 참조해 앞선 튜토리얼을 먼저 따라해보도록 한다.</p>\n<h3>개발 환경 설정: 텍스처로 사용할 이미지 추가하기</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\"ColorShader\"라는 이름의 프로젝트 항목을 오른쪽 클릭한 뒤 Add Texture > Add 2DTexture > [렌더몽키 설치 경로]/Examples/Media/Textures/Earth.jpg 메뉴를 선택해 이미지를 불러온다. 아니면, 만들어진 2DTexture를 오른쪽 클릭한 뒤 Edit... 메뉴를 선택해 원하는 이미지를 불러오도록 한다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eae019112a3854d87479a857a6432822/9b29b/add_earth_2d_texture.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"add_earth_2d_texture\"\n        title=\"add_earth_2d_texture\"\n        src=\"/static/eae019112a3854d87479a857a6432822/5a190/add_earth_2d_texture.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eae019112a3854d87479a857a6432822/772e8/add_earth_2d_texture.png 200w,\n/static/eae019112a3854d87479a857a6432822/e17e5/add_earth_2d_texture.png 400w,\n/static/eae019112a3854d87479a857a6432822/5a190/add_earth_2d_texture.png 800w,\n/static/eae019112a3854d87479a857a6432822/c1b63/add_earth_2d_texture.png 1200w,\n/static/eae019112a3854d87479a857a6432822/29007/add_earth_2d_texture.png 1600w,\n/static/eae019112a3854d87479a857a6432822/9b29b/add_earth_2d_texture.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>추가된 2DTexture의 이름을 \"DiffuseMap\"으로 변경한다. F2를 누르거나 항목을 오른쪽 클릭하고 Rename 메뉴를 선택하는 것으로 항목의 이름을 변경할 수 있다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fe605a10a0b3d73c0c999b68d706a66a/9b29b/rename_earth_2d_texture.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"rename_earth_2d_texture\"\n        title=\"rename_earth_2d_texture\"\n        src=\"/static/fe605a10a0b3d73c0c999b68d706a66a/5a190/rename_earth_2d_texture.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fe605a10a0b3d73c0c999b68d706a66a/772e8/rename_earth_2d_texture.png 200w,\n/static/fe605a10a0b3d73c0c999b68d706a66a/e17e5/rename_earth_2d_texture.png 400w,\n/static/fe605a10a0b3d73c0c999b68d706a66a/5a190/rename_earth_2d_texture.png 800w,\n/static/fe605a10a0b3d73c0c999b68d706a66a/c1b63/rename_earth_2d_texture.png 1200w,\n/static/fe605a10a0b3d73c0c999b68d706a66a/29007/rename_earth_2d_texture.png 1600w,\n/static/fe605a10a0b3d73c0c999b68d706a66a/9b29b/rename_earth_2d_texture.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>개발 환경 설정: 텍스처 개체 추가하기</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>왼쪽 Workspace 창에서 \"Pass 0\" 항목을 오른쪽 클릭한 뒤 Add Texture Object > DiffuseMap으로 방금 위에서 추가한 텍스처 이미지를 선택한다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8f54c78e160bb97a46b66465d027a616/9b29b/add_texture_object.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"add_texture_object\"\n        title=\"add_texture_object\"\n        src=\"/static/8f54c78e160bb97a46b66465d027a616/5a190/add_texture_object.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8f54c78e160bb97a46b66465d027a616/772e8/add_texture_object.png 200w,\n/static/8f54c78e160bb97a46b66465d027a616/e17e5/add_texture_object.png 400w,\n/static/8f54c78e160bb97a46b66465d027a616/5a190/add_texture_object.png 800w,\n/static/8f54c78e160bb97a46b66465d027a616/c1b63/add_texture_object.png 1200w,\n/static/8f54c78e160bb97a46b66465d027a616/29007/add_texture_object.png 1600w,\n/static/8f54c78e160bb97a46b66465d027a616/9b29b/add_texture_object.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>생성된 텍스트 개체의 이름을 \"Texture0\"에서 \"DiffuseSampler\"로 변경한다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8eb9670aa7749f88dac960b49d164958/9b29b/diffuse_sampler_added.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"diffuse_sampler_added\"\n        title=\"diffuse_sampler_added\"\n        src=\"/static/8eb9670aa7749f88dac960b49d164958/5a190/diffuse_sampler_added.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8eb9670aa7749f88dac960b49d164958/772e8/diffuse_sampler_added.png 200w,\n/static/8eb9670aa7749f88dac960b49d164958/e17e5/diffuse_sampler_added.png 400w,\n/static/8eb9670aa7749f88dac960b49d164958/5a190/diffuse_sampler_added.png 800w,\n/static/8eb9670aa7749f88dac960b49d164958/c1b63/diffuse_sampler_added.png 1200w,\n/static/8eb9670aa7749f88dac960b49d164958/29007/diffuse_sampler_added.png 1600w,\n/static/8eb9670aa7749f88dac960b49d164958/9b29b/diffuse_sampler_added.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>이제 셰이더로 텍스처를 불러올 준비가 되었다</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>정점 셰이더 함수 구현: UV 좌표를 포함한 정점 위치 정보를 반환</h3>\n<p>본래 정점 셰이더가 하는 일은 <strong>정점의 위치를 투영공간으로 변환시키는 것</strong>이다. 그러면 정점의 위치 정보를 반환해야 할 텐데, 정점 셰이더에서는 꼭 위치 정보<strong>만</strong> 반환해야 하는 것은 아니다. 정점 셰이더는 보간기(interpolator)라는 장치를 통해 정점 위치 이외의 정보를 보간해준다. 따라서 여기서 정점 셰이더가 할 일은 <code class=\"language-text\">Output.mTexCoord = Input.mTexCoord;</code>라는 문장을 통해 UV 좌표를 정점 위치 정보와 함꼐 반환하는 일뿐이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"hlsl\"><pre class=\"language-hlsl\"><code class=\"language-hlsl\"><span class=\"token keyword\">float4x4</span> gWorldMatrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">float4x4</span> gViewMatrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">float4x4</span> gProjectionMatrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">VS_INPUT</span> \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span> mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> POSITION<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">float2</span> mTexCoord <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> TEXCOORD0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">VS_OUTPUT</span> \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span> mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> POSITION<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">float2</span> mTexCoord <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> TEXCOORD0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nVS_OUTPUT <span class=\"token function\">vs_main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> VS_INPUT Input <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   VS_OUTPUT Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n   Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> Input<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gWorldMatrix <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>         <span class=\"token comment\">// 월드 행렬로 공간 변환</span>\n   Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gViewMatrix <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>          <span class=\"token comment\">// 뷰 행렬로 공간 변환</span>\n   Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gProjectionMatrix <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// 투영 행렬로 공간 변환</span>\n   \n   Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mTexCoord <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Input<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mTexCoord<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   \n   <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>픽셀 셰이더 함수 구현: 텍스처 이미지에서 텍셀(texel)을 계산한 뒤 반환</h3>\n<p>여기서 픽셀 셰이더가 할 일은 <strong>텍스처 이미지에서 텍셀(texel)을 계산한 뒤 그 색을 화면에 출력하는 것</strong>이다. 이를 위해 존재하는 HLSL 내장 함수 <code class=\"language-text\">tex2D</code>는 매개변수로 1) 텍스처 샘플러(texture sampler)와 2) UV 좌표를 전달받아 그 계산 결과로서의 텍셀 값을 반환해준다. 이제 픽셀 셰이더가 할 일은 이 계산된 텍셀 값을 반환하는 일뿐이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"hlsl\"><pre class=\"language-hlsl\"><code class=\"language-hlsl\">sampler2D DiffuseSampler<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PS_INPUT</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">float2</span> mTexCoord<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> TEXCOORD0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span> <span class=\"token function\">ps_main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> PS_INPUT Input <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> COLOR\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span> albedo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">tex2D</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>DiffuseSampler<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Input<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mTexCoord<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> albedo<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>rgba<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>완성된 텍스처맵핑 예제</h3>\n<p>마침내 텍스처맵핑이 적용된 셰이더가 완성되었다. 다들 각자 생애 첫 텍스처맵핑을 구현한 기쁨을 만끽하도록 하자</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c13729fcb3b3a80ab843136f2dfd5b9a/9b29b/texture_mapping_completed.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"texture_mapping_completed\"\n        title=\"texture_mapping_completed\"\n        src=\"/static/c13729fcb3b3a80ab843136f2dfd5b9a/5a190/texture_mapping_completed.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c13729fcb3b3a80ab843136f2dfd5b9a/772e8/texture_mapping_completed.png 200w,\n/static/c13729fcb3b3a80ab843136f2dfd5b9a/e17e5/texture_mapping_completed.png 400w,\n/static/c13729fcb3b3a80ab843136f2dfd5b9a/5a190/texture_mapping_completed.png 800w,\n/static/c13729fcb3b3a80ab843136f2dfd5b9a/c1b63/texture_mapping_completed.png 1200w,\n/static/c13729fcb3b3a80ab843136f2dfd5b9a/29007/texture_mapping_completed.png 1600w,\n/static/c13729fcb3b3a80ab843136f2dfd5b9a/9b29b/texture_mapping_completed.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>만약 실습을 진행하는데 어려움이 있는 경우에는 미리 완성된 다음 프로젝트 파일을 다운로드 받은 뒤 렌더몽키를 통해 열고 직접 분석해보도록 한다: <a href=\"https://github.com/sungkukpark/shader_programming_intro/blob/master/samples/texture_mapping/texture_mapping.zip\">다운로드 받기</a></p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"[Shader] Pope Kim의 셰이더 프로그래밍 입문 (3): 텍스처매핑"},"excerpt":"본 포스팅은 Pope Kim의 『셰이더 프로그래밍 입문 (한빛미디어, 2012)』의 Part 1의 Chapter 3에 해당하는 내용(p. 75-92)을 요약하기 위해 작성되었다. 학습 목표 셰이더를 통해 모델에 텍스처를 입히는 텍스처매핑(texture…"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/shader_programming_intro_3/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216","63159454"]}